  <v-card>
    <v-toolbar
      v-if="fillHeader"

      <v-toolbar-title>

export default {
  name: 'VBasicCard',
  props: {
    fillHeader: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: true,
    },
    toolbarHeight: {

      default: undefined,
    },
    title: {
      type: String,
    },
  },

</script>
